<dashboard version="1.1" theme="dark" script="scripts/frontend_count.js">
  <label>Machine Data Lab</label>
  <row>
    <panel>
      <html>
        <h1 style="font-weight: bold;">Win an iPhone, just by being here. </h1>
        <div class="three-col">
          <div>This application was created to give you a hands-on experience of what an analytical application is on a Big Data platform. Explore the dashboard, see the data move in real time, and understand how data tells the story.</div>
          <div>Participation is free, open to all, and fully transparent. The draw will take place when we reach 2,000 registered participants.</div>
          <div>The winner is selected through a deterministic algorithm based on a hash of each participant's email address. Once the milestone is hit, we will publish both the algorithm and the full list of hashed emails. Good luck!</div>
        </div>
        <style>
            #mapa_expandido .panel-body {
                height: 1180px !important; 
            }
            
            #mapa_expandido .shared-reportvisualizer {
                height: 1180px !important;
            }
            
            #mapa_expandido .viz-controller {
                height: 1180px !important;
            }
            
            #mapa_expandido .shared-map-lazymap {
                height: 100% !important;
            }
            
            #mapa_expandido .shared-map {
                height: 100% !important;
            }
            
            #mapping{
                height: 1180px;
            }
          
            text.single-result {
                font-size: 120px !important;
            }
            
            .dashboard-row {
                position: relative !important;
                display: contents;
            }
            
            
            #mapa_expandido{
                position: absolute !important;
                right: 0 !important;
                width: 50% !important;
                height: 1180px !important;
                z-index: 10;
            }
            
            
            #value, #value1, #value2, #value0{
              width: 20% !important;
            }
            
            #graph, #graph2, #pie_cities, #graph0{
              width: 30% !important;
            }
            

            #graph .dashboard-panel {
                height: 291px !important;
            }
          
           .three-col {
              display: grid;
              grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
              gap: 2rem;
              margin-top: 0.8rem;
              font-size: 17px;
              line-height: 1.6;
            }
            
            .dashboard-row .dashboard-panel .panel-head h3 {
              font-size: 18px;
            }
            
            #pie_cities .highcharts-series-group {
                mask: radial-gradient(circle, transparent 55%, black 56%);
                -webkit-mask: radial-gradient(circle, transparent 55%, black 56%);
            }
            
            .svg-container{
              top: -20px !important;
            }
          
            .checkbox-row {
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
                gap: 0.6rem;
                margin-top: 1.2rem;
                cursor: pointer;
            }
            
            .checkbox-row input[type="checkbox"] {
                appearance: none;
                -webkit-appearance: none;
                width: 18px;
                height: 18px;
                min-width: 18px;
                border: 2px solid #7FACFF;
                border-radius: 3px;
                background-color: transparent;
                cursor: pointer;
                position: relative;
            }
            
            .checkbox-row input[type="checkbox"]:checked {
                background-color: #ffffff;
                border-color: #7FACFF;
            }
            
            .checkbox-row input[type="checkbox"]:checked::after {
                content: "";
                position: absolute;
                left: 5px;
                top: 0px;
                width: 4px;
                height: 10px;
                border: 3px solid #7FACFF;
                border-top: none;
                border-left: none;
                transform: rotate(45deg);
            }

            #popUpBtn, #submitRulesBtn {
              background-color: #7FACFF;
              color: white;
              border: none;
              padding: 8px 20px;
              font-size: 17px;
              border-radius: 4px;
              cursor: pointer;
              margin-left: 0;
              margin-top: 10px;
            }

            #registerBtn, #submitRulesBtn {
              background-color: #7FACFF;
              color: white;
              border: none;
              padding: 6px 16px;
              font-size: 17px;
              border-radius: 4px;
              cursor: pointer;
              margin-left: 0;
            }
        
            #registerBtn:hover, #popUpBtn:hover, #submitRulesBtn:hover {
              background-color: #656DA1;
            }
            
            #closePopupBtn, #cancelRulesBtn{
              position: absolute;
              right: 125px;
              background-color: lightcoral;
              border-radius: 4px;
              border: none;
              padding: 6px 16px;
              font-size: 17px;
              color: white;
            }
            
            #closePopupBtn:hover, #cancelRulesBtn:hover{
              background-color: #f6aeae; 
            }
            
            .popup-overlay {
              position: fixed;
              top: 0;
              left: 0;
              width: 100%;
              height: 100%;
              background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
              z-index: 9999;
            }
          
            .popup-box {
              background: #505050;
              width: 450px;
              padding: 30px;
              border-radius: 6px;
              position: absolute;
              top: 50%;
              left: 50%;
              transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            }
            
            .popuprules-overlay {
              position: fixed;
              top: 0;
              left: 0;
              width: 100%;
              height: 100%;
              background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
              z-index: 9999;
            }
          
            .popuprules-box {
              background: #505050;
              width: 600px;
              padding: 20px;
              border-radius: 6px;
              position: absolute;
              top: 50%;
              left: 50%;
              transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            }
          </style>
          <!-- 
          # <label for="emailInput">Insert your email:</label>
          <input type="text" id="emailInput" placeholder="you@example.com"/>
          <button id="registerBtn" type="button">Register</button ># -->
          <button id="popUpBtn" type="button">Register</button>
          <!--#<div id="stateMessage" style="margin:10px; color:#333;"/># -->
          <div id="emailPopup" class="popup-overlay" style="display:none;">
            <div class="popup-box">
                <h3 style="font-size: 17px;">Insert your name:</h3>
                <input type="text" id="nameInput" placeholder="Your name" style="width:100%; margin-bottom:10px; background-color: #000000; font-size: 17px;"/>
                <h3 style="font-size: 17px;">Insert your email:</h3>
                <input type="text" id="emailInput" placeholder="you@example.com" style="width:100%; margin-bottom:10px; background-color: #000000; font-size: 17px;"/>
                <div id="popupMessage" style="margin-bottom:10px; color:#333; font-size: medium;"/>
                <div style="display: ruby-text;">
                  <button id="closePopupBtn" class="btn btn-secondary">Cancel</button>
                  <button id="registerBtn" type="button" class="btn btn-success" style="right: 30px; position: absolute;">Submit</button>
                </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <style>
            #statusMessage { margin-top:12px; padding:12px 16px; border-radius:6px; font-size:14px; display:none; }
            #statusMessage.pending { background-color:#3a3000; border-left:4px solid #f8be34; color:#f8be34; }
            #statusMessage.validated { background-color:#003a00; border-left:4px solid #53a051; color:#53a051; }
          </style>
          <div id="statusMessage"/>
      </html>
    </panel>
  </row>
